{"tid":1633053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我請求你哋5分鐘睇！ 《孫子兵法》說","createTime":"2019-10-07T02:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:47:32.000Z","uid":291625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8c307471372a4da8bd93f95ad7f8e3d8781c274c","tid":1633053,"uid":291625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:08:10.000Z","msg":"「&hellip;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">途有所不由，軍有所不擊，城有所不攻，地有所不爭，君命有所不受</span></strong></span>。」就是因為在戰場上戰況瞬息萬變，戰機稍縱即逝，為爭取決定性勝利，聰明的領導者都要有〝有所為與有所不為〞的觀念！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">1.國際輿論開始轉風向：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\nBBC:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4tAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=f5b3f4e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&h=20132a5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548</a><br />\nAnti-government marches in Hong Kong have ended in rioting, with attacks on government offices, a metro station and businesses with ties to mainland China.<br />\n<br />\nCNN:<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4tAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=4549f253\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=53844d7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html</a><br />\nViolent protests which began Friday stretched into the early hours of Saturday, beyond the midnight deadline when the new anti-mask regulations began. They spread out across the city and soon devolved into violent clashes, with protesters throwing petrol bombs and police responding with pepper spray and tear gas.<br />\n<br />\nUN rights chief :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F10%2F06%2Fun-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence%2F&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4tAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=1c4c5b80\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/</a><br />\nUN human rights chief Michelle Bachelet said Saturday she was &ldquo;troubled&rdquo; by Hong Kong&rsquo;s increasingly violent pro-democracy protests<br />\n<br />\n開始無人話警察武力不對等，國際開始支持港府。再係咁落去，美國人權及民主法案好可能被否決！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">2.再睇睇先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CkoVJOK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCkoVJOK.jpg&h=b7d56215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">3.重點！重點！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n其實777知佢仲未可以動用到緊急法，但佢特登令我地自己營造緊急打仗狀態！<br />\n到司法覆核既時候佢既律師就可以同法庭講 &ldquo;係呀之前都可能未justified 但依家就唔同啦&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n星期五第一個司法覆核就係咁輸<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個覆核成功，成條緊急法都會被廢除，個盒唔會再有人有得玩。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">4.最後</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尋日前線拉咗好多人，我相信有一啲手續需要時間去平復心情！大家都俾人拉晒邊個會再幫佢哋搵律師，forward 嗰啲相啊自己諗下！<br />\n我尋日見到我都俾人拉嘅都係啲好細個好細個呢轉先，你知唔知我個心幾痛！ 我係成年人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期五司法覆核前！ 民主法案通過前！<br />\n俾和理非/大律師做野先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">最後，天琦bb講過</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rq4FawH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRq4FawH.jpg&h=8df4d834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n最後，我愛你地！ 煲底再見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0195bb0fcfdfd939d57a48c9ab29250ce36bee4d","tid":1633053,"uid":291625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:09:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自推十下<br />\n和理非出場！ 乖！態武要休息</span>"},{"pid":"4761a6e5bb5adbe14849e4e7f40496ca8807eeb4","tid":1633053,"uid":291625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:10:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自推2/10<br />\n和理非出場！ 乖！態武要休息</span>"},{"pid":"01d5b2e2424d4af3a8cd26a204c1f23a5488c1da","tid":1633053,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:16:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92f3472500cf4a614ab5bd1ec09e97a63c18030d","tid":1633053,"uid":291625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:26:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自推十下3/10<br />\n和理非出場！ 乖！勇武要休息</span>"},{"pid":"a6ae4ca6e75bfa7a4db9cdb975b3ccf1c4be4f2a","tid":1633053,"uid":291625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:27:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自推十下4/10<br />\n和理非出場！ 乖！勇武要休息</span>"},{"pid":"d085476c3b9a5fc5d57b3acf86da2e753f147e99","tid":1633053,"uid":291625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:29:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自推十下5/10<br />\n和理非出場！ 乖！勇武要休息</span>"},{"pid":"fea3ed336f3c84d26ce21c604640cccab3f2087e","tid":1633053,"uid":291625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:29:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自推十下6/10<br />\n和理非出場！ 乖！勇武要休息</span>"},{"pid":"241032bea7271337c7c515ee8dacbec54a20fa29","tid":1633053,"uid":291625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:35:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自推十下6/10<br />\n和理非出場！ 乖！勇武要休息</span>"},{"pid":"6ab0532479605c30acbf14ac89991d8b2a6fe3f8","tid":1633053,"uid":291625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:37:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自推十下8/10<br />\n和理非出場！ 乖！勇武要休息</span>"},{"pid":"f98ddd983dee345d13203d6547e6499b21373b17","tid":1633053,"uid":282891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d745b7c36c7346b19c4464316dc039184b1c3b","tid":1633053,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:41:19.000Z","msg":"罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但和勇合一係成場運動既關鍵，兩樣一齊做唔撚得？講緊既係，拆鐵係唔撚會影響人權法，或所謂既民意，但對政權、運動係現時有最大既影響力"},{"pid":"85a32f6c6bd4d51530fa2ab67a23c41a9e944927","tid":1633053,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:47:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">二百幾萬<strong>和理非</strong> 係時候一齊出手</span><br />\n<br />\n銀髮軍師 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非加入 戰況大增千倍的</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新戰術</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1613583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1613583</a>"}]}